Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A1是土耳其青釉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A2是青铜釉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3是鹭釉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就照这样继续下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢你的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来很忙的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在什么地方工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在库双庵的偏室造好了 我在帮忙弄那边的花盆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库双庵的话...是镰仓的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用一所古宅改造而成的一家很好的店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在一个很不错的地方工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是托理花小姐的福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她介绍了很多人给我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来理花很看重你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在是再加把劲的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花现在是在西班牙的天空下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在居然在巴伦西亚美术馆里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她真的很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花小姐上周去了西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而真山没有一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道出发前他们之间发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在接理花偶尔会打来的电话时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话的声音和以前有点不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一种平静和深沉交杂在一起的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他已经被温柔地接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 山田 我带你去一个好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 利达你要留下来看家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个好地方……吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「欢迎光临」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「平日半价」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「澡堂」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「健康大陆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 美和子小姐 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一起尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那……那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和子小姐……那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是舒服啊 蔷薇水果浴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菠……菠萝……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把身体泡暖之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就做擦垢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\fs18}把身体的污垢擦除 有点像用磨沙洗脸的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注:笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会认真为你们服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦垢中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擦垢结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好光滑 就像去了一层皮一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 去下一个地方吧 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田 很好看吧 这条连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者该说是穆穆袍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\fs16}穆穆袍:Muumuu 原为夏威夷的民族服装 后演变为寛松的连衣裙 60年代起作为夏季家庭服装在日本得到普及
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是躺着的还是做运动的  都一样穿着穆穆袍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢乐健康大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 总觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着这衣服老让我想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着这种花纹图案的穆穆袍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连回想那些难过的事都变得困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来向美食进军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先来点生啤和毛豆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是为了帮我打起精神来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在想是从哪里来的香味呢 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是金挂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当这个香味弥漫在大街上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年学园祭的准备就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在校园橘黄色的路灯下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金桂的香味中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找着那个喜欢的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几次跑去那个可能碰到他的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想多看他几眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多听听他的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久久地 久久地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香啊 我最喜欢这花了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田喜欢金桂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 喝吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完以后我们去游泳 按摩 日耳曼尼亚按摩浴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是全程服务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\shad0}「哇 是山田小姐 欢迎欢迎」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一觉睡到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 野宫 你打来真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 山田在你那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是让她发泄了一下 做了健康大陆的全程服务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发泄了一下 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不就是真山和理花的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了一会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系 她已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露着美丽的大腿 几乎只穿着单薄的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\shad0}「哇 野宫先生真是的」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个诚实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就交给你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可爱的女孩子不管什么时候我都欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 真山还真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有魅力 身材又好的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24小时跟她待在一起却没有对她产生丁点儿的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常的重视这女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常的重视这女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个纯情女孩为什么不给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来以为她没跟我联系是因为现在过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道居然是这样情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田小姐出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说她向你求救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野宫你要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在那边哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野……野宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过一段时间我就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 在这之前不要再一个人哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再在别人的面前哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么……到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个沙丘的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森 森 森田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能随便拿别人的东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了拿到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在拼命地积攒生活补贴和打工的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月可是关键时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用仅有的100元买的麭包皮 我打算拿它撑到下个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本君 阿久的蒸面包给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 那是阿久的中饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 竹本君 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 脏 死 了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很脏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏到要那么急着用肥皂冲洗的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在别人面前演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢别人的东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上已经全黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本你最近真是越来越嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你反倒怪起我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许在这里吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果打扰到阿久做画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一阵风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,40)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3a&HFF&\3c&H000000&}{\shad0}二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,40)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3a&HFF&\3c&H000000&}{\shad0}二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,40)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3a&HFF&\3c&H000000&}{\shad0}二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,40)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3a&HFF&\3c&H000000&}{\shad0}二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 我的钱 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 别跑 现在就来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有那么多钱为什么还要抢我的饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 全在了 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田 你到底在打什么工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赚了这么多钱却不见你用过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么拼命工作到底为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你很久了 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早点让你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能半永久地从全世界的儿童身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每月收集五十元的完美系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 白山也感动得哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 白山应该是因为别的原因而哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 玩笑到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿忍 下个月之前还能给我一枝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一枝? 单位是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白山 把半永久压缩在一年之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把对象从孩子变为30岁前未婚人士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把资产再调整一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熏 有好好睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多睡一会吧 不然大脑会迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做得太过显眼 会被察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被你说教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下还差多少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本 你太极端了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是为了快点拿到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要把生活费都搭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长 这个好吃 米粒在我身体里运动着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 吃吧 多吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么那么急着要驾照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想到我家来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁上学的时候拿到驾照就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了旅行做准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 今天我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去澡堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的时候给你买你喜欢的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 学长 你的恩情我一辈子都不会忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 真山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长为什么现在还住在那个公寓里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在工作应该能找个更好的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有些放不下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说是为了防止出现意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现意外 那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还不知道要不要回来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候我在好几本书上读到了这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不管是什么人都会有三次机遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后成年之后我就察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦机遇降临的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也似乎只会单纯地想着有钱没钱的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长 难道说你存了很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来没钱的人只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本你没关系 因为你还是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长已经获得机遇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己喜欢的女人出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至少可以对她说一句 什么都不要想好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想要些存款
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真……真山学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才实在是太直白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认 我说的那些……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长 你真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去澡堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把身上这臭味洗掉的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉它吧 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我刚才说的那些傻话忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山学长你正闪闪发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己喜欢的女人出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至少可以对她说一句 什么都不要想好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想要些存款
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 我很认同真山学长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也仅仅是认同而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 还是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思啊 山田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你特别跑过来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道美和子到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 高井户先生 我会等她的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,175)}{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fs18}{\shad0}「啊 是山田小姐 呜」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利达 利达 可爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(515,105)}{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fs18}{\shad0}「哇 是新歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,190)}{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fs18}{\shad0}山田小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腿后面也毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 利达 你说美和子小姐去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在健康大陆真的很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金挂下喝着啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金挂花的……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田 实在撑不下去的时候叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在撑不下去的时候……叫我……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\shad0}「哈啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了 美和子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H208ED4&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\shad0}「野宫 野宫」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利达 你过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗是吗 很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很想你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回旋踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己的心一下被他看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就这么跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实本来是想给他打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多话想对他倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很多事情想问他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么很讨厌自己的这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前对真山的所有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将成为谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管旁人看我多可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有对他的这份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冰冷又明亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想心里一直想着真山而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 然而
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他回来了 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时又很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 我们从未去过海边
